  "description": "An icon is a [sign](./sign.md) that represents its object by resemblance. The [representamen](./representamen.md) shares some quality or structural feature with the thing it stands for — a portrait resembles the person depicted, a map resembles the territory, a diagram resembles the structure it represents.",
